MAJOR UPGRADES:

Portable Panel:
* Added a page system for multiple controls.
* Page 1: Map Controls
* Page 2: Avatar Scale & Player Locator
* Page 3: Scavenger Hunt UI

Avatar Scale allows you to go up to 100 meters. In the event you cannot reset it, you can always use your Expression Menu to reset your scale.
There is a button on the front of the panel, but in my testing, I had to be precise on selecting it

Please be aware that large scales will fuck with your collisions and you may fall through the map despite your mesh touching the floor. This is because your collider does NOT scale with your mesh scale.

Multi Jump:
* You can now multi-jump and a sound plays when you do so.
* You can adjust the volume using the Portable Panel

AudioZones:
* Allows you to talk to those in the stage area and vice versa.
* You must be inside an Audio Zone to be able to talk to those on the stage. Current Audio Zones are MMD Song Selection (denoted by green carpet), and the spectator theatre
* You can also use the Michael Phone (microphone) to talk to EVERYONE regardless of position. Abuse will lead to this being locked to supporters only.

Player Locator:
* Allows you to find players. Current areas are: Spawn, MMD Song Selection, Bridge, Spectator Theatre, and the Stage
* Found on page 1 in the Portable Panel

Scavenger Hunt:
* Some of you might have noticed some condoms around the map. Now they actually have a use! Practice safe interactions & find them all to win a prize!
* UI found on Page 2
* If you know about Big Rigs Off the Road Racing, you will enjoy the prize.

Pickupables:
* Added some pickups for you to toss and hurt your friends with phantom sense! (DO NOT. You can toggle the objects to prevent people from throwing them towards you)
* Will be adding more objects in the future.

